ROX-Filer is a fast and powerful graphical file manager for the
X Window System. You can use it as a small and fast filer within
your current desktop, or get it to manage your pinboard, panels
and applications...

Features:
- Fast scanning of directories (in the background)
- Uncluttered display (popup menus are used throughout)
- Background file operations (copy, move, link, delete, permissions, find)
- Powerful expression-based find feature with on-line quick reference
- Mounts and unmounts filesystems (just Shift-Click on the mount point)
- Supports the XDND protocol (drag-and-drop file loading) and the
XDS extension (drag-and-drop saving)
- VFS support allows browsing around inside zip files and other archives
- Fully configurable from the Options dialog box
- User-defined key bindings for all menu entries
- A pop-up minibuffer for navigating with tab completion and shell commands
- Full printable manual provided (PostScript format)
